---
title: Hearty Mushroom, Chorizo & Spinach Risotto with Almonds, Garden Salad & Truffle Oil
description: This comforting mushroom and chorizo risotto becomes rich and full of flavour with sharp grated Parmesan. Add a crisp cucumber salad and almonds to perfectly round out the meal.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6561da6ec79d741428512bff-3cdfb589.jpeg
